{"tid":895241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子上廁所GG了　蟒蛇從馬桶鑽出咬爆睪丸 圖","createTime":"2018-11-09T04:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T14:22:10.000Z","uid":72009,"like":67,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8ed0b15654abc44d3e57609a6babb9dcfd7336","tid":895241,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"泰國一名救援人員昨日在臉書上分享一段影片，他指出他前去一戶人家抓蟒蛇，但這條蟒蛇很特殊，咬爆一名男子的下體睪丸，導致男子當場濺血GG。<br />\n<br />\n據泰國《khaosod》報導，這名救援人員安亞武在臉書上發布這段捕蛇影片。據悉男主角在家中上廁所時，突然感到下體一陣「絕頂疼痛」，他仔細一看，竟是一條蟒蛇從馬桶的洞鑽出，更直接咬爆他的睪丸，導致他鮮血長流。男子隨後被家人緊急送醫，目前狀況不明。<br />\n<br />\n安亞武也指出，蟒蛇「犯案」後並未逃跑，而是繼續躲在馬桶的洞內。當救援人員抵達現場捕蛇時，這條蟒蛇還在洞口探頭探腦，之後救援人員把燈關掉，才成功「引蛇出洞」順利捕捉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181109/640_3608f1f2ba34b15b88e7f06e86280f97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181109%2F640_3608f1f2ba34b15b88e7f06e86280f97.jpg&h=bbf27c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6cdc39a01f407995e2ea33569545361cd67c4ea","tid":895241,"uid":67779,"like":294,"dislike":1,"score":293,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:44:09.000Z","msg":"隔離post就斷J<br />\n呢個post就爆蛋<br />\n<br />\n我仲要連續睇哂兩個<br />\n我好撚痛呀屌"},{"pid":"0940f40b2ed05aec70e2b4a8f3fa86bb0ec605ff","tid":895241,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:46:22.000Z","msg":"好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdee405dac53f3f56916e7d5d3575376a20fdc86","tid":895241,"uid":69213,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:51:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33bbce7c0f79dcc449b6e18a2d5f40f0e20cdad0","tid":895241,"uid":82434,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:52:44.000Z","msg":"餵條蛇屎屎尿尿 咬袋袋好公平 好合理"},{"pid":"b274c171a0baec1923c967fefd7e487d0b4fcd4d","tid":895241,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci